data.name: ANESTHESIA CIRCUITS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% PVC and 100% DEHP-FREE PVC and Silicone

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Available with diﬀerent types of Wye connectors and elbows
- With and Without Water Traps

## PERFORMANCE
- Light weight reduces torque on endotracheal tube
- High transparency for good visibility
- Good tenacity and low compliance
- Well designed tubing prevents tube collapse
- Cuﬀed connections ensure good sealing
